description: The Code Moon NFT collection is inspired by the exciting vision for the future of humanity. In this collection, you will discover thrilling illustrations depicting scenes from life on the Moon, where people have retreated following the ecological challenges of Earth. Each image reveals fascinating details of life and technological progress on the Moon, presented through exquisite artwork and innovative design. Become a part of this unique collection and preserve the moment from the beginning of a new era for humanity. Every NFT from this collection can be bought and sold on OKX NFT, ensuring seamless access to a global marketplace for collectors and traders alike.
name: Code Moon
